article_id:1724,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Adjustment to the Weekly Bonus Obtainable from Certain Quests,image_path:,message:<div>Starting at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1604296800"></span>, twinkling sand will be obtainable from the weekly bonus of certain quests. See the following for details.</div><div><br></div><div>■Additional Bonus</div><div>・Twinkling Sand &times; 1</div><div>Note: Players will earn double this amount while the 7-Day Pack (Double Bonus) is in effect.</div><div><br></div><div>■Eligible Quests</div><div>・Advanced Dragon Trials</div><div>High Midgardsormr&#39;s Trial: Standard/Expert/Master</div><div>High Mercury&#39;s Trial: Standard/Expert/Master</div><div>High Brunhilda&#39;s Trial: Standard/Expert/Master</div><div>High Jupiter&#39;s Trial: Standard/Expert/Master</div><div>High Zodiark&#39;s Trial: Standard/Expert/Master</div><div><br></div><div>・The Agito Uprising</div><div>Volk&#39;s Wrath: Standard/Expert/Master</div><div>Ciella&#39;s Wrath: Standard/Expert/Master</div><div>Ayaha &amp; Otoha&#39;s Wrath: Standard/Expert/Master</div><div>Kai Yan&#39;s Wrath: Standard/Expert/Master</div><div>Tartarus&#39;s Wrath: Standard/Expert</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1603681200,update_time1603681258